WEBVTT

01:39.583 --> 01:40.583
So?

01:41.625 --> 01:42.458
What?

01:42.541 --> 01:43.583
What did you see?

01:46.416 --> 01:47.333
A chubby one.

01:49.583 --> 01:50.583
And dark skinned.

01:53.041 --> 01:53.916
Dark skinned?

01:56.500 --> 01:58.083
So he was yours.

01:58.416 --> 01:59.250
Dark skin.

02:00.166 --> 02:01.000
Yes.

02:23.208 --> 02:24.541
Were my tits big?

02:27.500 --> 02:28.333
Huge.

02:36.083 --> 02:37.250
You saw the father?

02:37.791 --> 02:39.166
No. I didn't see him.

02:48.166 --> 02:49.541
What're we going to do?

02:52.083 --> 02:53.333
We'll figure it out.

02:56.833 --> 02:58.000
Come here.

02:59.416 --> 03:00.250
Come on.

03:09.250 --> 03:10.250
-Stop.
-What?

03:10.458 --> 03:11.583
Let's play again.

03:12.500 --> 03:13.333
All right.

03:20.083 --> 03:20.916
One.

03:21.791 --> 03:22.625
Two.

03:23.291 --> 03:24.291
Three.

06:01.958 --> 06:03.208
Ma'am?

06:10.791 --> 06:15.250
BASED ON THE PLAY
"The Wind in a Violin"

06:19.041 --> 06:21.208
Darío, get up, hurry.

06:30.708 --> 06:31.916
Ma'am, get up.

06:32.875 --> 06:33.708
Nora?

06:33.958 --> 06:34.791
Yes.

06:36.166 --> 06:37.208
What time is it?

06:38.000 --> 06:40.750
It's 9:15, ma'am.
The alarm's gone off.

06:42.500 --> 06:44.500
This piece of trash didn't go off!

06:47.916 --> 06:49.041
Goddamn it!

06:49.791 --> 06:51.875
-Hand me the phone.
-Yes.

06:53.875 --> 06:56.333
-Here. There it is.
-I can't see a thing.

06:57.916 --> 06:59.125
Here. Find Esteban.

07:05.208 --> 07:07.250
There are many that say "Esteban."

07:08.000 --> 07:09.250
Check on "Logistics."

07:10.125 --> 07:11.458
Esteban, Logistics.

07:11.541 --> 07:12.541
"Logistics."

07:19.125 --> 07:20.916
Darío is asleep.

07:22.791 --> 07:23.708
Hello, Esteban?

07:24.375 --> 07:26.500
One moment... One moment,
one moment.

07:26.666 --> 07:28.875
Wake him. He has class
and can't skip it.

07:28.958 --> 07:29.791
I'll wake him.

07:30.041 --> 07:31.583
And he has therapy later.

07:31.666 --> 07:34.791
Sorry. No, I've got a bad signal.

07:36.750 --> 07:40.625
No. I'm running late
at the faculty, with Darío.

07:41.541 --> 07:44.250
No, he fought with a teacher.
He's on edge.

07:44.916 --> 07:48.541
I'm currently in a meeting
with the head of the program.

07:50.166 --> 07:53.416
Still, everything's in the e-mail
I sent you last night.

07:54.208 --> 07:55.916
I sent it to you last night.

07:56.791 --> 07:58.208
That doesn't make sense.

07:59.875 --> 08:02.375
No, no, no!
You know what I need, Esteban? Explain.

08:03.125 --> 08:04.083
You understand?

08:04.541 --> 08:05.708
Say I didn't skip it.

08:06.291 --> 08:07.833
Exactly!

08:08.583 --> 08:10.125
Can you explain to them?

08:11.208 --> 08:12.250
You'll try?

08:12.750 --> 08:14.958
Okay. So, you'll try.

08:15.500 --> 08:16.333
Fantastic!

08:16.791 --> 08:20.041
Tell me something, Esteban,
why don't you try and go to hell as well?

08:21.000 --> 08:23.166
Son of a bitch!

08:25.375 --> 08:27.125
He says he'll try, he'll try.

09:43.875 --> 09:45.250
Thanks.

09:56.875 --> 09:57.791
Who is it?

09:58.666 --> 10:00.250
Hey, Santiago. It's Darío.

10:00.750 --> 10:01.583
Come on in.

10:07.916 --> 10:12.041
Yes, yes, yes. I'm calm.
I'm focusing on my projects.

10:14.208 --> 10:16.291
-Do you still smoke?
-Pot?

10:16.875 --> 10:20.458
As usual, very little. Thing is,
the weed dried out, so...

10:20.541 --> 10:22.916
I don't have pot left.
Don't have any.

10:25.125 --> 10:27.291
Everything's coming together, right?

10:29.000 --> 10:31.791
You have a job,
the weeds dried out...

10:32.333 --> 10:33.375
All's better with Mom.

10:34.916 --> 10:38.333
We just began yet you're already
talking about your mother.

10:39.250 --> 10:42.875
This is therapy, isn't it?
It's normal to talk about mothers.

10:43.208 --> 10:44.041
Yeah?

10:44.958 --> 10:46.208
So, you're an expert?

10:47.291 --> 10:48.125
Just a bit.

10:49.416 --> 10:50.833
I always repeat myself.

10:51.083 --> 10:52.250
And so do you.

10:54.375 --> 10:56.666
I like the job you're doing.

10:56.750 --> 10:57.625
I like it.

10:58.791 --> 11:00.708
But I find it unfair having to pay you

11:00.791 --> 11:03.083
when we're almost
on the same intellectual level.

11:06.833 --> 11:07.666
Santiago, I...

11:08.000 --> 11:10.541
I want you to feel comfortable
with me,

11:10.625 --> 11:12.708
in case you need help
with patients.

11:14.208 --> 11:15.333
I've been thinking.

11:16.291 --> 11:18.416
We can get together at a bar.

11:18.500 --> 11:20.750
And I can share my advice

11:20.833 --> 11:23.541
with the toughest cases, especially.
Yeah?

11:24.125 --> 11:26.375
Or you can record the session

11:26.458 --> 11:28.833
on your phone
so we can hear it together.

11:28.916 --> 11:30.041
Don't forget,

11:30.125 --> 11:32.208
we have to think of the patient.

11:33.583 --> 11:37.500
Think of his needs. You get me?
We can't both go on like this.

11:37.583 --> 11:39.583
You say one thing,
and I have to correct you.

11:39.708 --> 11:42.375
No, no, no.
We need to be a team,

11:42.916 --> 11:44.125
and work together.

11:45.458 --> 11:47.291
So, what do you think? Tell me.

11:48.333 --> 11:49.166
I think...

11:50.750 --> 11:53.208
that your mentality is very immature.

11:53.583 --> 11:55.000
-Mature?
-Immature.

11:56.041 --> 11:59.750
And I also think you still depend strongly
on your mother.

12:00.083 --> 12:03.125
You also don't make use
of this space as you should.

12:03.791 --> 12:07.250
And I strongly can't think
of how you could help me.

12:12.333 --> 12:13.291
As a secretary?

12:14.958 --> 12:15.958
Was I not clear?

12:17.916 --> 12:20.958
In order to do this, Darío,
you require studies.

12:21.916 --> 12:23.541
Yes? It requires effort.

12:25.166 --> 12:26.000
Are we done?

12:28.458 --> 12:29.708
Yes, we're done. Yes.

12:38.208 --> 12:40.291
Can you hand me a big book?

12:42.083 --> 12:42.916
Yes.

12:44.416 --> 12:46.583
-This one?
-No. Bigger than this one.

12:52.833 --> 12:53.666
Like that.

13:00.750 --> 13:01.708
What happened?

13:01.875 --> 13:04.000
I just felt a little dizzy, that's all.

13:04.083 --> 13:05.041
-Again?
-No!

13:05.125 --> 13:07.375
It's nothing. Nothing.

13:07.583 --> 13:08.791
When's your checkup?

13:09.583 --> 13:11.958
-I'll ask Norita.
-Yeah, ask her.

13:12.041 --> 13:13.041
All right.

13:14.583 --> 13:15.958
-Hey.
-What?

13:16.458 --> 13:18.083
You got to look after this bump.

13:20.541 --> 13:21.875
Got something in mind?

13:23.166 --> 13:25.125
Seems there's an alumni reunion.

13:25.541 --> 13:26.375
We could go.

13:27.291 --> 13:28.916
-Where?
-In a club.

13:30.083 --> 13:30.916
A club?

13:37.250 --> 13:38.916
Try first, it has very little salt.

13:39.083 --> 13:40.375
You might want more.

13:40.500 --> 13:41.875
I can't eat salt.

13:42.666 --> 13:44.083
-Only a little.
-No, ma.

13:45.541 --> 13:47.083
Else, it tastes bland.

13:49.333 --> 13:50.750
It doesn't taste bland.

13:59.458 --> 14:00.666
When's the checkup?

14:03.333 --> 14:04.541
On Thursday.

14:08.083 --> 14:10.208
I won't add salt on tomorrow's food.

14:10.500 --> 14:12.625
I'm not cooking any more fried food.

14:17.500 --> 14:18.333
All right.

14:25.708 --> 14:26.541
Water, Nora?

14:29.833 --> 14:30.666
Nora.

15:26.500 --> 15:28.000
-Hi.
-Hi.

15:28.750 --> 15:30.666
I brought the Inspired
and flowery model.

15:30.750 --> 15:31.583
What?

15:31.833 --> 15:33.166
I brought you flowers.

15:33.541 --> 15:34.375
What?

15:35.500 --> 15:39.541
The Inspired model's over there
along with the flowery design.

15:39.625 --> 15:40.458
All right.

16:05.208 --> 16:06.458
Hi, honey.

16:07.000 --> 16:08.125
-Hi.
-No, Mom, back off.

16:08.208 --> 16:11.250
-Why are you here?
-Why wouldn't I be?

16:12.833 --> 16:13.791
It's so hot.

16:14.541 --> 16:15.416
Yeah.

16:15.500 --> 16:17.958
Can't they set up a waiting room
with AC?

16:18.666 --> 16:19.541
She's coming!

16:20.000 --> 16:21.500
Look, look...

16:31.333 --> 16:32.166
Courses with?

16:33.666 --> 16:34.500
Sorrati.

16:34.583 --> 16:36.458
Not that son of a bitch!

16:36.541 --> 16:37.916
Biggest son of a bitch.

16:38.625 --> 16:41.000
I bet there's no one
who didn't retake that course,

16:41.083 --> 16:43.666
-or at least three times. What a bastard.
-Only Germán.

16:45.458 --> 16:49.083
What about Germán?
This is his first time under Sorrati.

16:49.791 --> 16:51.375
Still dunno if he passed. Relax.

16:52.541 --> 16:54.125
Did you send the planners?

16:55.291 --> 16:56.125
Yes.

16:56.208 --> 16:58.208
Yes? There wasn't a problem?

16:59.083 --> 17:01.916
Good. I'm glad.

17:04.083 --> 17:06.208
I asked you for a project
and paid in advance.

17:06.458 --> 17:08.040
And it was a hefty sum.

17:09.040 --> 17:10.750
You didn't send a single one!
Not one!

17:10.833 --> 17:12.708
-Lower your voice.
-No, I won't!

17:18.915 --> 17:19.915
You had therapy?

17:21.000 --> 17:22.083
Didn't I tell you?

17:22.165 --> 17:23.708
-I won't go anymore.
-What?

17:23.790 --> 17:25.665
I'm not going anymore! Come on.

17:25.750 --> 17:27.000
I've been discharged.

17:28.708 --> 17:29.958
Discharged?

17:31.708 --> 17:34.791
"You're discharged"?
Did the therapist tell you that?

17:35.416 --> 17:37.583
We came to that decision together.

17:38.416 --> 17:40.500
Why should I explain to you?
Why tell you?

17:40.583 --> 17:41.625
Look, look, look.

17:43.166 --> 17:45.250
What joy!

17:45.791 --> 17:48.541
-It's a...
-There he is! Look! There!

17:48.625 --> 17:49.750
Go, honey, hit him!

17:50.208 --> 17:52.166
Harder! Hit him!

17:52.500 --> 17:53.750
What a waste!

17:54.708 --> 17:55.666
Higher!

18:43.625 --> 18:45.625
What is it? Looking for something?

18:45.708 --> 18:47.625
Something of Celeste's.

18:48.041 --> 18:50.375
There's nothing there.
That's my drawer.

18:50.458 --> 18:51.958
Tidy up and close it.

18:53.083 --> 18:56.500
-I only want to see the results.
-They're not there. Why?

18:59.458 --> 19:01.333
I want to know how she's doing.

19:01.541 --> 19:02.708
She's doing fine.

19:03.416 --> 19:04.833
Tell me where they are.

19:06.000 --> 19:07.833
Do you understand those things?

19:08.083 --> 19:09.041
No, not at all.

19:09.791 --> 19:12.125
But I can show a doctor
and ask his opinion.

19:12.625 --> 19:14.958
No, I take her to the doctor
'cause I'm her mother.

19:15.041 --> 19:16.291
You won't do a thing.

19:17.166 --> 19:18.291
Close that drawer.

19:19.625 --> 19:21.333
Nora, I care for your daughter.

19:22.125 --> 19:23.250
And want to help.

19:43.041 --> 19:43.875
Who is it?

19:43.958 --> 19:45.208
Mercedes Oliverti.

19:49.416 --> 19:50.541
I'm Darío's mother.

19:50.625 --> 19:52.583
-Yes. Eh...
-Remember me?

19:52.833 --> 19:55.583
Right, I'm very busy at the moment.
What do you need?

19:55.666 --> 19:56.791
Where's the divan?

19:57.125 --> 19:59.041
-What divan?
-Your divan, doctor.

19:59.208 --> 20:01.916
Hold, on. What do you need, ma'am?
Wait a minute...

20:02.000 --> 20:04.541
To have a little chat.
I only have time now.

20:04.708 --> 20:05.708
Chat about what?

20:33.750 --> 20:35.916
He doesn't know it,
but there was a twin.

20:37.291 --> 20:39.708
Darío? Does he have a brother?

20:43.875 --> 20:45.750
Actually, during childbirth...

20:47.416 --> 20:48.458
the other baby...

20:51.000 --> 20:52.916
Actually, I call him Darío, too.

20:53.375 --> 20:56.416
I don't know why, but...
I gave him the same name.

20:59.583 --> 21:00.458
Well...

21:02.375 --> 21:04.833
During birth, Darío came out first.

21:07.291 --> 21:09.166
And he accidentally...

21:10.458 --> 21:13.541
...tied the cord
around the other babe.

21:13.625 --> 21:15.000
Around the brother.

21:18.083 --> 21:19.208
He strangled him.

21:25.916 --> 21:28.333
You think this is why he's stuck?

21:30.791 --> 21:33.625
Is that why he can't move on?

21:35.625 --> 21:36.458
No.

21:36.750 --> 21:37.583
I doubt it.

21:41.125 --> 21:42.250
I never told him.

21:43.916 --> 21:44.750
But that's it.

21:46.125 --> 21:47.666
That's how he came to be.

21:49.958 --> 21:51.125
Through murder.

22:06.166 --> 22:08.458
Will you ask him to come back?

22:09.291 --> 22:10.125
No.

22:10.208 --> 22:12.666
I doubt that's a good idea-- What?

22:12.875 --> 22:14.958
Hi, honey!

22:15.791 --> 22:17.791
-Don't say you're here.
-You're at the party?

22:17.875 --> 22:20.458
No, no, no.
I'm having a drink with friends.

22:21.875 --> 22:23.708
Yes, darling. What is it?

22:24.541 --> 22:26.208
I get it, okay. That's fine.

22:26.500 --> 22:28.500
No, don't worry, I won't butt in.

22:29.250 --> 22:32.208
There's food if you feel hungry.
In the fridge.

22:32.875 --> 22:35.958
There's a delicious squash pie
with onions.

22:36.416 --> 22:38.583
Heat it a minute in the microwave.

22:38.666 --> 22:40.208
-Or try it cold.
-Or eat it cold.

22:40.291 --> 22:42.958
-He's an adult.
-Yes, you're an adult, Darío.

22:43.541 --> 22:46.458
Take care, honey.
Should we have lunch tomorrow?

22:46.916 --> 22:50.083
He hung up. No, no.
I forgot to tell you something.

22:50.166 --> 22:51.583
What?

22:54.416 --> 22:57.291
Don't you have something here

22:57.708 --> 22:59.458
to give Darío?

23:00.000 --> 23:02.458
No. I don't do prescriptions.
Can't medicate him.

23:02.541 --> 23:05.541
No, I don't mean a prescription, doctor.
Like a job.

23:06.416 --> 23:08.208
A job? That thing with the job again?

23:08.291 --> 23:09.333
Who do you think I am?

23:09.416 --> 23:10.791
-Any job?
-No!

23:10.916 --> 23:12.458
-Think about it.
-I won't.

23:12.541 --> 23:15.333
-I work alone.
-We could reach an understanding.

23:15.583 --> 23:17.375
What kind of understanding?

23:18.708 --> 23:21.000
I give you the money for his salary.

23:23.916 --> 23:25.250
And more, of course.

23:28.291 --> 23:29.333
Think about it.

23:42.416 --> 23:46.166
So cute, so cute.

23:51.250 --> 23:52.083
Beautiful.

23:58.833 --> 24:00.166
You're wearing makeup?

24:00.291 --> 24:01.125
Yes.

24:01.625 --> 24:03.375
Haven't seen you like that.

24:03.750 --> 24:04.583
You will now.

24:05.583 --> 24:07.625
It's all right. You're two faced.

24:07.875 --> 24:09.625
-Where is it?
-North.

24:10.458 --> 24:12.291
-But where?
-I'll take you.

24:15.416 --> 24:16.750
How are we getting in?

24:17.125 --> 24:20.083
With the guy from work.
He's going to the club.

24:21.250 --> 24:23.916
-Did you tell him?
-No. What would I tell him?

24:41.000 --> 24:43.125
Tell us, come on!

24:43.583 --> 24:47.333
Were bricks and domes
used in the Byzantine Empire?

24:47.916 --> 24:48.916
No!

24:49.541 --> 24:50.458
No!

24:50.875 --> 24:54.125
Seemed impossible. I didn't think so.
But I didn't know that answer.

24:54.208 --> 24:55.958
I didn't study that part exactly.

24:56.083 --> 24:57.166
So I drew a blank.

24:57.250 --> 25:00.125
I didn't know what to do.
And right then, guys,

25:00.458 --> 25:03.375
I remembered
that the night before, my father

25:03.458 --> 25:05.791
had given me a penholder.

25:05.875 --> 25:08.500
A fancy one, made of gold,
or it was golden, at least.

25:09.083 --> 25:10.625
So I said: "Sorrati,

25:11.208 --> 25:12.625
begging your pardon,

25:12.708 --> 25:14.875
I'd like to give you this
for your dedication,

25:14.958 --> 25:18.208
and love for architecture,
and blah, blah, blah,

25:18.416 --> 25:20.041
as a gift."

25:20.416 --> 25:22.250
So, I gave him the penholder

25:22.791 --> 25:26.041
and he stares at me.
Looks me straight in the eye

25:26.166 --> 25:28.875
and says: "So, architect Albert,

25:28.958 --> 25:30.291
do you want a B+?"

25:32.125 --> 25:33.500
Success!

25:35.791 --> 25:38.000
Good move with that penholder.

25:38.208 --> 25:41.625
-I saw that. He likes you.
-He likes me a lot apparently.

25:42.250 --> 25:43.958
I didn't plan ahead.

25:44.833 --> 25:47.375
Hold on, hold on.
So, you have him the penholder,

25:47.458 --> 25:48.958
and what did he ask then?

25:49.041 --> 25:51.583
No... What?
He didn't ask me anything.

25:51.666 --> 25:54.000
He asked me
about the Byzantine Empire,

25:54.666 --> 25:57.041
and I gave him the penholder.
He didn't ask anything.

26:05.000 --> 26:06.333
Excuse me.

26:09.208 --> 26:11.875
Excuse me,
could I have a gin and tonic?

26:23.333 --> 26:24.916
One gin and tonic, please.

28:28.333 --> 28:29.166
That one?

28:29.750 --> 28:31.833
-Which one?
-That one. The tall one.

28:32.083 --> 28:33.166
Tall and slim guy.

28:34.291 --> 28:37.625
Him? No. Awful, don't like him.

28:38.250 --> 28:40.333
No, no. Do you like him?

28:53.625 --> 28:54.458
You like him?

28:55.083 --> 28:55.916
Yes.

28:57.291 --> 28:58.125
Sure?

29:01.291 --> 29:02.125
I'll get him.

29:06.375 --> 29:07.208
Count.

29:07.708 --> 29:10.041
One, two, three.

29:26.958 --> 29:29.125
You have a big house.

29:32.541 --> 29:34.375
It's not mine. It's my mom's.

29:35.041 --> 29:38.750
I'm making a few changes at home,
and I have my studio there...

29:47.625 --> 29:48.750
What're you having?

29:48.916 --> 29:50.458
-I'm not thirsty.
-Really?

29:50.625 --> 29:52.250
No drinks? Look what I got.

29:52.333 --> 29:54.000
For you, for you, for you.

29:56.833 --> 29:57.916
-No?
-No, thanks.

29:59.666 --> 30:01.083
I'll have a drink.

30:06.500 --> 30:07.833
Sure you won't drink?

30:08.208 --> 30:09.041
No.

30:09.375 --> 30:10.458
Not even a little?

30:11.000 --> 30:11.833
A small taste?

30:22.208 --> 30:24.041
It's all right. Look it's fine, fine.

30:24.125 --> 30:24.958
It's fine.

30:38.333 --> 30:40.750
Come, come, come.

30:41.041 --> 30:42.500
Come, come, come.

31:12.625 --> 31:13.500
You sure?

31:13.916 --> 31:14.750
Yes.

31:15.541 --> 31:17.250
-Let me.
-All right.

31:48.833 --> 31:50.458
-Wait.
-Give it to me...

31:50.541 --> 31:52.583
No, no. What is it? What is it?

31:58.166 --> 31:59.375
Stop.

32:02.750 --> 32:04.875
-Stop. What is it?
-No condom.

32:05.416 --> 32:07.375
