41:50.250 --> 41:51.083
Right.

41:51.333 --> 41:52.625
-There he is.
-Hey, Santiago.

41:52.708 --> 41:55.000
-Thanks, Darío. How are you?
-Fine.

41:57.208 --> 41:59.583
-I'm sorry this was unexpected.
-It's all right.

42:00.000 --> 42:01.166
