42:57.583 --> 43:00.458
-I'll call.
-It's something personal, right?

43:00.541 --> 43:01.750
This was between us.

43:01.833 --> 43:04.500
-Nora, please go. Go.
-Yes, thank you.

43:04.666 --> 43:05.833
-Excuse me.
-Yes.

43:09.291 --> 43:12.458
What's up with your call
and some message?

43:16.291 --> 43:20.416
Look, I was thinking
about our chat the other day,

43:22.166 --> 43:25.000
