What with college and all that.

43:44.916 --> 43:47.708
I don't get why an aide, that's all.

43:49.458 --> 43:51.625
Well, it's close
so you'll manage your schedule

43:51.708 --> 43:53.666
and won't need to go far.
Besides,

43:54.208 --> 43:56.583
I need you to lend me a hand
with some things...

43:56.708 --> 43:58.625
Excuse me. I was just passing.

43:58.958 --> 44:01.041
I didn't hear what you just said.

44:02.666 --> 44:05.666
I was telling Darío that I needed an aide
for the office.

44:05.958 --> 44:07.291
-That's odd.
-Why?

44:07.791 --> 44:11.458
