45:08.625 --> 45:09.458
All right?

45:11.625 --> 45:13.708
-What's wrong?
-I don't understand.

45:20.000 --> 45:20.833
Look, Darío.

45:22.666 --> 45:24.000
We want to help you.

45:24.458 --> 45:25.625
